full_content:
Function: acl_copy_entry
URL: https://www.qnx.com/developers/docs/7.1/com.qnx.doc.neutrino.lib_ref/topic/a/acl_copy_entry.html
Synopsis: int acl_copy_entry( acl_entry_t dest_d,
Headers: #include <sys/acl.h>
Parameters:
  - dest_d: The descriptor for the destination entry.
  - src_d: The descriptor for the entry that you want to copy.
Examples:
Example 1:
#include <sys/acl.h>

int acl_copy_entry( acl_entry_t dest_d,
                    acl_entry_t src_d );
